data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Call for details! This recently built home it’s ready for new owners! This lovely open floor plan one story home has so much to offer. Near the front of the home, you’ll find a full bedroom that would be ideal for an office. The remaining spare bedrooms and primary bedroom or separated in this ideal split floor plan. The kitchen, dining and living offer a lot of open space for entertaining, family and friends. The gorgeous kitchen has ample cabinetry and a lovely light color scheme. The drop zone in the hall is perfect for shoes and backpacks! Check out the pics of the large pie-shaped backyard! So much space for your people and pets! The oversized covered back patio has been extended with concrete for more storage space. Public OPEN HOUSE Saturday 11/18/23 2-4 PM! Call today for a showing!
